                                                                                                                                 2                                                                                        NATION BRIEFS
                                      
	 New Delhi, June 10: T.C.A. Anant, a Delhi School of Economics professor, is the new chief statistician of the country.           ant will replace Pronab Sen who will soon retire after a three-year tenure. Anant will also hold the rank of secretary, the National Statistical Commission, with concurrent charge as secretary, the ministry of statistics and programme implementation, an official statement said.          ant has done his PhD from Cornell University in Game Theory, Econometrics and Industrial Economics. The appointment will be for five years from the date of assuming office.                   
	 New Delhi: The Centre has decided to raise the retirement age of postgraduate teachers in nursing institutions from 60 to 65 years.                  
	 Singapore, June 10 (PTI): An Indian businessman was sentenced to a weeks jail and fined $2,100 (Rs 70,000) today for molesting a 19-year-old hotel trainee in on February 6. Udaya Kumar Purushottaman Chembottu, 50, admitted his guilt. Earlier, the victim had seen Chembottu molesting another hotel employee, a charge taken into consideration by the court.                   
	 Panaji (PTI): A Goa court has rejected the anticipatory bail plea by former tourism minister Fransisco Mickey Pacheco for his alleged involvement in the death of a friend, Nadia Torrado. Pacheco is now likely to approach the high court with the plea. Nadia, 28, allegedly consumed poison on May 15 and died after being treated for 15 days.                   
	 Bhubaneswar: Bhubaneswar may soon be accorded world heritage city status by Unesco. This was revealed by Armoogum Parsuramen, director of Unescos Delhi office.                                                                                                                                              
